{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was probably still the old line which was passing from south Warsaw to north Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they still had it, it passing by, but it wouldn't stop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were trams then used by-- well, there were private companies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They started having trams which were used in the ghetto, and they were horse trams.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were coaches.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So to say it was a kind of a large wagon painted, I think, white and blue, if I remember correctly, with two horses.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were-- there were a few lines like that inside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I think not all that many people went in the trams.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was, however, a lot of rickshaws.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were just rickshaws which were cycle rickshaws, which was a little open cart with the kind of an armchair with places for three people, maybe, sitting one alongside another with bicycle wheels to, to a tricycle with bicycle wheels and a-- and a wheel behind, and the rickshaw, which was-- which was the most-- as I remember, it was the most common way of transport.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who pu--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who drove the rickshaw?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rickshaw driver.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was the man who-- it was like a taxi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the way-- it was the taxi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And apart from that, there were carts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were pushing things on carts, on wheelbarrows, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So practically, it was a completely-- there was this impression of crowd.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was crowd everywhere, crowd on the roads, crowd on the pavements, masses and masses of people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then they had as well there were all kinds of stands which were-- there were-- people were selling things, you know, like selling something to eat or their own possessions and so on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the conditions were really very, very difficult and crowded.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
